content: DeliTracker was created in 1992 and played this file on the Amiga operating system, it ceased in 2000 but the DeliPlayer program was created to be emulated on the Windows operating system.

description: Audio File created to contain audio composed by David Whittaker for games on the Amiga operating system; used in Commodore Amiga games but can be played by specific players.
